                  <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt text-danger me-2"></i>
                  İbn-i Sina Mah. Havaalanı Yolu Bulvarı No:214 Şahinbey/Gaziantep
                </p>
                <p class="card-text">
                  <i class="fas fa-phone text-danger me-2"></i>
                  <a href="tel:03422352864" class="text-dark text-decoration-none">0342 235 2864</a>
